{"tid":918772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Plum大裁員】Plum走上大屠殺之路 皆因亂使錢","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T12:12:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5755a3817e0a5c595f882057d50c0a515972e0","tid":918772,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305578_b4c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305578_b4c4.jpg&h=9c763512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有10萬用戶的外賣平台Plum，火速搶佔市場，然後火速裁員又裁員，招致香港區業務幾乎「炒晒所有人」的命運。讓Plum走上困境的，最大原因是亂使錢。<br />\n<br />\n成立不足一年的Plum，高峰期香港達到200名員工，Startup之中屬少見。Plum聯合創辦人張漢樑早前本報接受訪問時承認，公司早期用人手處理大量工序，又聘請大量推廣人員，於8、9月公司停止增長，便於9月大手進行第一波裁員。<br />\n<br />\nPlum常以高薪招人，初期曾以高時薪聘請推廣員。據悉，曾有兩個月，單計用於派傳單推廣員的開支便超過百萬。"},{"pid":"5242a0549b6a88adbcb1217d41faa83899825dce","tid":918772,"uid":133641,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"人哋外國都未做得住，香港市場細點會賺到錢"},{"pid":"f8e43782af801505030136f80e29185ccb3c4910","tid":918772,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"做呢類系統門檻同要求太低，市場同類型服務又多，基本上請學生/廢青做parttime就差唔多，養冰做市場都on撚9"},{"pid":"25ad3b8a26617c7fbc96810a9370c9c512c65125","tid":918772,"uid":99420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6af8a1dfca4e8151158291ebeaa54f66e634062","tid":918772,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;派傳單推廣員&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d9936f50fcadc112dfa12d478909d8c657769f7f","tid":918772,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25ad3b8a26617c7fbc96810a9370c9c512c65125","tid":918772,"uid":99420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy